snippet.title: Wario Land 3 Walkthrough: Intro
snippet.description:
I'm back! I used to be DoomDragon14400, but after months of no-uploading and a Golden Sun Walkthrough that never came, I decided to close my account, but now I've decided to be reborn with a new name and new plans... 

Well, whatever, this is going to be a Wario Land 3 Walkthrough, a game I had for many years. I decided to play it again and soon I came up with the idea of doing a walkthrough, so, hope you enjoy!
